          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37155865/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37155865/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/queeniepku/" class=" " title="queenie">queenie</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37155865">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37155865/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p37155865-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">2012年第一次翻中译，隐约觉得不对劲。今年上课重读原著，把中译翻出来看了一眼，第一页第一段就译错：
Big Brotherly social program  ≠ “大的社会”计划
minority groups  ≠ 少数利益集团
government regulation of business  ≠ 政府制定商业规则

 </span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-02-10 04:39</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                2012年第一次翻中译，隐约觉得不对劲。今年上课重读原著，把中译翻出来看了一眼，第一页第一段就译错：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Big Brotherly social program  ≠ “大的社会”计划<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>minority groups  ≠ 少数利益集团<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>government regulation of business  ≠ 政府制定商业规则
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p37155865-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p37155865-2.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
